WorkItem.Description:
Try this:

a {
	color:green;
	:hover {
		color:red;
	}
}


should generate:

a {
  color: green;
}
a:hover {
  color: red;
}

but instead generates:

a {
  color: green;
}
a :hover {
  color: red;
}

With a space before the :hover, so the browser loses the hover effect.
Same thing with any other css pseudoclass

Thanks for the project, love it.
